hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: I can't hear you very well essential oils toenail fungus As a fan of the original (I was 19 when it first came out), the announcement of a remake hit me hard. Remakes aren't supposed to be done of films you remember seeing in the movie theater when you were young - they're supposed to be done of old films that your parents went to. I think a lot of the anger about the remake/reboot is based on people who are realizing now that they're the old ones.
